dataIdInfo.idAbs: This layer represents county parks for LaCrosse County, Wisconsin in 2016.[La Crosse County Parks parcel mapping of La Crosse County, Wisconsin represented in a GIS spatial database. Areas mapped include incorporated and unincorporated muinicipalities of La Crosse County. La Crosse County utilized the tax parcels shapefile and taxdata system to map the park properties. Spatial (positional) accuracy ranges in value depending on the source data. Areas lacking monumentation and/or survey records may not be accurate. This mapping provides a useful representation of the geometry and topology of county park parcels. It is not meant to be used for the determination of land ownership or be in any way a substitute for a land survey.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The purpose of this map coverage is to provide a digital map layer of county park properties and their associated text attributes and annotation.]
